{"tid":476439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"精神病院治療「歇斯底里」女病人 恐怖照片曝光","createTime":"2017-11-22T04:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T07:45:50.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02c9442d95fbd7658f1641467a781bb6440d4be7","tid":476439,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"精神病院治療「歇斯底里」女病人 恐怖照片曝光<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171121/1056908.htm?t=%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%87%E6%96%AF%E5%BA%95%E9%87%8C%E3%80%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA++%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171121%2F1056908.htm%3Ft%3D%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2599%2582%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AD%2587%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25BA%2595%25E9%2587%258C%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%2B%2B%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589&d=0RPuTf6AeM3Pf2%2BE24Au0KNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=5ca518f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171121/1056908.htm?t=%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%87%E6%96%AF%E5%BA%95%E9%87%8C%E3%80%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA++%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2940/d2940399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2940%2Fd2940399.jpg&h=7a43550a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲《硝石庫醫院寫真集》，曝光了19世紀時精神病院的接受「歇斯底里」治療的女病患畫面。（圖／翻攝自鏡報)<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n這些讓人如噩夢般難忘的照片，曝光了19世紀時在精神病院的接受「歇斯底里症」(hysteria)治療的女病患真實畫面。 她們的「症狀」包括性衝動、緊張和煩躁。<br />\n<br />\n這些照片來自1870年代法國巴黎「硝石庫慈善醫院」( Salpetriere Hospital)。院方的醫護人員 試圖治癒她們、瞭解她們的不安狀態。至19世紀中葉時，這家醫院已收容了5000名出現各種「歇斯底里」症状的女病患，尤其是精神病患。<br />\n<br />\n數世紀以來，女性的「歇斯底里症」是經常出現的醫學診斷結果。它被認為是只會在女性身上出現的疾病，因為當的醫師認為這跟 女性的子宮異常有關。但被「確診」是「病患」的女性，往往只是因為呼吸急促、水腫、甚至只是調皮搗蛋，就會被強迫接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n其他會被強迫接受入院治療的「症狀」還包括暈眩、緊張、性衝動、失眠、易怒等。許多人就在上述情況下被家人送到醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n神經學家夏科特(Jean-Marie Charcot)被視為是研究「歇斯底里症」 的先驅，他收集的「歇斯底里症」女病人的照片，連同他的文章，在1878年結集成《硝石庫醫院寫真集》(Iconographie photographique de la Salpetriere) 一書出版。"},{"pid":"38225d26ee01a274e31386886d0311da516913b7","tid":476439,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:08:49.000Z","msg":"驅魔人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beedd86f4a4df0465dbd281484bf2cac4f48292a","tid":476439,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"Biohazard 7"},{"pid":"5f42946e3c67a36201a15fe40c7c266f67187ed7","tid":476439,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"Only one way out"},{"pid":"2e31d43a2b231f18aaa865582e81042694504634","tid":476439,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"Outlast"},{"pid":"5269626e5947e78191284fa90b9991d6917936b4","tid":476439,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Only one way out</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哇!!!"},{"pid":"91cde8fb04692baf105d93b87635d81729274a4a","tid":476439,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"性衝動都係病症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972998eaf022167bca305630fd6d9c15e1f53504","tid":476439,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性衝動都係病症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5761fcf6d9dd43d9580ffea4c6d28b6f82fb7b","tid":476439,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>性衝動都係病症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n快點強姦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc59987fddaf9f2cfd2b638e35e5310d68c7d843","tid":476439,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6facf87314569f07423aab0f3a020fa19c6f4624","tid":476439,"uid":72694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"歐洲在19世紀前的兩千年裡一直認為歇斯底里是由於女性子宮擾動、遊走或倒錯造成的。當時認為懷孕可以消除該症狀。在19世紀中晚期，該病主要指性功能障礙，<span style=\"color: red;\">治療方法是用手、振動器或噴水進行生殖器按摩，使患者達到性高潮。</span>19世紀末至20世紀初，醫學界逐漸認識到該病是一種心理疾病，20世紀中期以後，歇斯底里症被細分為許多精神疾病，醫學界已逐漸停止使用該詞，轉而使用更精確的詞彙描述不同症狀，如轉換障礙和分離障礙。"},{"pid":"d5223fd4bb036311ecc7578e36b2bbb570d6db3f","tid":476439,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲在19世紀前的兩千年裡一直認為歇斯底里是由於女性子宮擾動、遊走或倒錯造成的。當時認為懷孕可以消除該症狀。在19世紀中晚期，該病主要指性功能障礙，<span style=\"color: red;\">治療方法是用手、振動器或噴水進行生殖器按摩，使患者達到性高潮。</span>19世紀末至20世紀初，醫學界逐漸認識到該病是一種心理疾病，20世紀中期以後，歇斯底里症被細分為許多精神疾病，醫學界已逐漸停止使用該詞，轉而使用更精確的詞彙描述不同症狀，如轉換障礙和分離障礙。</blockquote><br />\n送佢地做雞就搞掂"}]}